data.title: CHEP Kroonstad
data.meta_description: CHEP offers you a complete line of wooden pallets, Reusable Plastic Containers (RPCs) - crates and bins, wooden bins, Intermediate Bulk Containers (IBCs), Auto boxes and inserts. This specific service centre however has the following products: Block & Bearer pallets / RPC crates / RPC bins / Wooden bins / IBCs / Auto boxes.  Should you want a product not available at this service centre, please contact us.
